		<div class="post" id="post-3762256">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,3762256)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-3762256">
																		Hey y&#039;all!
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226191" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;" >DarkStuff</a></span> <span class="odate time_1523134727 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Apr 2018 20:58</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3762256">
									

<p>And we're live! This has been quite the journey getting Wilson's Wildlife Solutions off the ground, and I can't thank the community enough for this opportunity. I mean, I only had to write two articles, and it just sort of <em>happened</em> from there. In particular, though, I have to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532150584" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;">Rimple</a></span>, because he gave me the beginnings of a draft that offhandedly mentioned &quot;Wilson's Wildlife Solutions&quot; just as a name for someone to call in <a href="/scp-3466">SCP-3466</a>. I took that and made it way, way bigger and weirder. So thank you! Thank you so much for that inspiration!</p>
<p>Anyways, I realize there is no &quot;how to write us&quot; section, and I thought about adding one, but I think the Introduction &amp; What We're All About sections <em>are</em> that. They tell you all you need to know before writing, and the way they are narrated gives you the typical Wilson's Wildlife tone. Other than that, even though we may not have GoI Formats or tales yet &#8212; key word, &quot;yet&quot; &#8212; the hub is 100% functional.</p>
<p>Also, expect an add-on to the hub at some point. I have some stuff I am writing, but it's a bit too esoteric for a generalized hub, so I'm going to make it and have this hub be its parent page. I'll keep what it actually is as a surprise for once it is up, but expect some cool &quot;bonus content&quot; for this hub page at some point in the future.</p>
<p>Well&#8230; that's all I have to say right now! Yay for Wilson's Wildlife! Yay for the chance to make it a hub! Yay yay yay!!</p>
<hr />
<p>SOME CREDITS:</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532150584" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;">Rimple</a></span> = Making the name and writing a very rough draft that inspired this whole mess.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532150584" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;">Weryllium</a></span> = Naming MTF Beta-4 the Castaways (ha ha what a funny dude).</li>
