<p>I love the idea of Wilson's Wildlife Solutions and I think I'd like to write something to be included in it. And I have a question about the organization:</p>
<p>Is the WWS the kind of organization to have a zoo or some other form of public building in order to showcase animals? I could see it going either way. The way I see it for the purposes of WWS, Boring is kinda like Sloth's Pit where anomalous stuff just kinda happens and everyone ignores it, but if that's not really how it is that's cool too.</p>
<p>Ahh I wanna write so much about this GOI. It seems really fun!</p>

							</div>

								
